data.description: Welcome Home to this 3 bed 2 full bath, beautiful Ridgewood home. Inside you will find many updates including flooring, carpet, paint, and a new gas fireplace. There is an addition room on the Lower level that could easily be a fourth bedroom! Partially finished basement with the possibility of a bedroom. Outside there is an inground pool with a brand new filter, pool pump, and privacy fence. Call today for a private showing. This one won't last long!Professional pictures coming soon!
